# mongo-datatables

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/mongo-datatables.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/mongo-datatables)
[![Downloads](https://static.pepy.tech/badge/mongo-datatables)](https://pepy.tech/project/mongo-datatables)
